{"type":"message","id":"d8eb57fa","parentId":"7562e25c","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:14:39.056Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_q8e5yqscfjvi_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 4239\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='' file='' new_len=0\r\n[mutation parse failed] old='' file='' new_len=0\r\n[master 15fc54d] pulse: 2026-03-24 131415\n 5 files changed, 215 insertions(+), 98 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 131415.md\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 131317.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 131415 - The CFI Compression Synthesis identified that three-dimensional filtering (CFI � 0.5 AND freq ? [3, 120)) correctly handles constant-format tokens, but the proposed hybrid scoring formula (CFI x min(1, freq/120)) needs validation to ensure it properly weights informative vs. metaprogramming tokens.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"crisp-lagoon","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 4239\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='' file='' new_len=0\r\n[mutation parse failed] old='' file='' new_len=0\r\n[master 15fc54d] pulse: 2026-03-24 131415\n 5 files changed, 215 insertions(+), 98 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 131415.md\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 131317.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 131415 - The CFI Compression Synthesis identified that three-dimensional filtering (CFI � 0.5 AND freq ? [3, 120)) correctly handles constant-format tokens, but the proposed hybrid scoring formula (CFI x min(1, freq/120)) needs validation to ensure it properly weights informative vs. metaprogramming tokens.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774372479052}}
{"type":"message","id":"2dbab1f6","parentId":"d8eb57fa","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:14:39.061Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_q8e5yqscfjvi_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"﻿# Pulse: 2026-03-24 131317\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\nRejected: research/strategy_c_experiment.ps1 (missing)\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLet me analyze the current state and determine the best concrete action to advance the goals.\r\n\r\nCurrent state:\r\n- Phase 0 and Phase 1 COMPLETE (architecture cross-analysis and integration spec)\r\n- CFI Compression Experiment completed with key findings\r\n- Key insight: Need hybrid CFI×Freq scoring (Strategy C)\r\n- Pending: Hybrid CFI×Freq scoring experiment, distinguishing constant format vs research trajectory, implementing CFI filtering\r\n\r\nThe next logical step based on the stated goals is to implement the hybrid scoring experiment (Strategy C). The formula is:\r\nscore(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n\r\nI should run this experiment on the pulse data. Let me look at the pulse data and implement this.\r\n\r\nActually, looking at the goals more carefully:\r\n1. The CFI compression synthesis document exists\r\n2. The next experiment is the hybrid CFI×Freq scoring (Strategy C)\r\n3. This should distinguish \"constant format\" from \"research trajectory\"\r\n\r\nThe most concrete action would be to implement the hybrid scoring formula on the pulse data and run the experiment. I should create a script or analysis that:\r\n1. Loads the pulse data\r\n2. Applies the hybrid scoring: score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n3. Compares this to the previous binary threshold approach\r\n4. Documents the results\r\n\r\nLet me check what files exist and implement this.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe CFI compression synthesis identified Strategy C (hybrid CFI×Freq^0.5) as the next experiment. The scoring formula is concrete: score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120). This needs to be implemented and tested against the pulse data to verify it correctly distinguishes constant-format tokens from research trajectories.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate hybrid scoring experiment (Strategy C) comparing CFI×Freq^0.5 scoring against previous binary thresholds, using the pulse token data to validate the approach.\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # Strategy C: Hybrid CFI×Freq Scoring Experiment\r\n## Date: 2026-03-24\r\n\r\n## Objective\r\nTest hybrid scoring formula that combines CFI and frequency as orthogonal signals:\r\n```\r\nscore(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Hypothesis\r\n- Constant-format tokens (freq≈160, CFI=1): score = 1.0 × 1.0 = 1.0 (BUT we filter by freq < 120)\r\n- Research trajectory tokens (freq<120, CFI>0.5): score = 0.5-1.0 × (freq/120)\r\n- This will naturally downweight constant tokens while preserving causal research tokens\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n| Token Type | freq | CFI | score | Pass? |\r\n|------------|------|-----|-------|-------|\r\n| \"for next instantiation\" | 160 | 1.00 | 1.33 | NO (freq≥120) |\r\n| \"Phase 1\" | 136 | 0.96 | 1.09 | NO (freq≥120) |\r\n| \"research\" | 45 | 0.72 | 0.27 | YES |\r\n| \"architecture\" | 23 | 0.68 | 0.13 | YES |\r\n\r\n## Experiment\r\n[TODO: Run on pulse_2026-03-24 data]\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # Strategy C: Hybrid CFI×Freq Scoring Experiment\r\n## Date: 2026-03-24\r\n\r\n## Objective\r\nTest hybrid scoring formula that combines CFI and frequency as orthogonal signals:\r\n```\r\nscore(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Hypothesis\r\n- Constant-format tokens (freq≈160, CFI=1): score = 1.0 × 1.0 = 1.0 (BUT we filter by freq < 120)\r\n- Research trajectory tokens (freq<120, CFI>0.5): score = 0.5-1.0 × (freq/120)\r\n- This will naturally downweight constant tokens while preserving causal research tokens\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n| Token Type | freq | CFI | score | Pass? |\r\n|------------|------|-----|-------|-------|\r\n| \"for next instantiation\" | 160 | 1.00 | 1.33 | NO (freq≥120) |\r\n| \"Phase 1\" | 136 | 0.96 | 1.09 | NO (freq≥120) |\r\n| \"research\" | 45 | 0.72 | 0.27 | YES |\r\n| \"architecture\" | 23 | 0.68 | 0.13 | YES |\r\n\r\n## Experiment\r\n[TODO: Run on pulse_2026-03-24 data]\r\n\r\n## Results\r\n[To be populated after experiment]\r\n\r\n## Conclusion\r\n[To be populated after experiment]\r\n```\r\nfile: research/CFI_STRATEGY_C_HYBRID.md\r\n```\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 13:13:36\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774372479056}}
